name: pytest-benchmark
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "3.0.0" %}

package:
  name: pytest-benchmark
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: pytest-benchmark-{{ version }}.zip
  url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/p/pytest-benchmark/pytest-benchmark-{{ version }}.zip
  md5: f8ab8e438f039366e3765168ad831b4c

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pytest >=2.6

  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pytest >=2.6

test:
  imports:
    - pytest_benchmark

about:
  home: https://github.com/ionelmc/pytest-benchmark
  license: BSD 2-clause
  summary: "A py.test fixture for benchmarking code"

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - juanlu001
